**Steps to Reproduce**:

```c#
public enum MyEnum { Default }
public MyEnum Method_Warning(MyEnum? val)
{
    bool hasValue = val.HasValue;
    if (!hasValue)
    {
        val = MyEnum.Default;
    }

    return val.Value; // warning CS8629: Nullable value type may be null.
}

public MyEnum Method_NoWarning(MyEnum? val)
{
    if (!val.HasValue)
    {
        val = MyEnum.Default;
    }

    return val.Value;
}
```
